body 
  h1 Treasure Hunt Game 
  h2 Avoid waking the Dragon
  img class="awake" id="dragon" src="https://img.myloview.com/murals/illustration-of-sleeping-dragon-400-47143510.jpg" alt="sleeping dragon"
  ul class="rules"
    li Click the boxes to reveal what is on the map.
    li If you click on the treasure, you sneak away with it and <span class="win">WIN!</span>
    li If you click on 5 alarms, the dragon wakes up and you <span class="lose">LOSE</span>
    li If you click on the dragon, he wakes up and you <span class="lose">LOSE!</span>
  br
  table.gameMap[border="5" ]
    tr
      td#0 onclick="treasure(0)" <span class="initial-value">?</span>
      td#1 onclick="treasure(1)" <span class="initial-value">?</span>
      td#2 onclick="treasure(2)" <span class="initial-value">?</span>
      td#3 onclick="treasure(3)" <span class="initial-value">?</span>
